Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ED
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Trailer
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.69,0:23:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又一艘現身此地的神祕戰艦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.92,0:23:42.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒙面的船長到底所言為何
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.32,0:23:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千秋的提議
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.67,0:23:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉香的決意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.63,0:23:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古老的海盜會議會復生嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.96,0:23:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手握著這一切關鍵的傳說中的廚師的真實身份是？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.00,0:23:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回 猛烈宇宙海賊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.92,0:23:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標！海賊巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.65,0:23:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬請期待
